+/**
+ * struct gbr - Guaranteed Bit Rate IE
+ * @base: Common IE header
+ * @ul_gbr: Uplink GBR in kilobits per second (network byte order)
+ * @dl_gbr: Downlink GBR in kilobits per second (network byte order)
